<p><b>How can I help?</b></p>

<p>Now there's a question we love to hear! Black & Yellow Pages was created because we wanted the service, not because we wanted to develop and maintain it. If you are a developer or designer, we can use all the help we can get. The code for Black & Yellow Pages is hosted at github, so please feel free to make your own Black & Yellow Pages, help us improve this one, or completely blow us out of the water with a better application!</p>

<p>If you're looking to make a splash, there is work to be done in trust metrics and web of trust ratings. Ideally, we would like to see multiple user ratings for all our users, and will room to display them all right on each user's page. Readers can make up their own minds about weighting the different trust statistics.</p>